.Tp alarm(2)
\fIAlarm\fP, \fIAlarmTime\fP, and \fISleep\fP
.Tp pause(2)
used for suspension by \fISleep\fP
.Tp time(2)
\fIGetTime\fP
.Tp times(2)
\fIGetProcessTimes\fP, \fIRealTime\fP and \fICPUTime\fP
.Te
